import getListStudents from './0-get_list_students';

console.log(getListStudents());

const getStudentIdsSum = (arr) => arr.reduce((prev, curr) => prev.id, 0);
export default getStudentIdsSum;

const getStudentIdsSum = (arr) => arr.reduce((acc, curr) => acc + curr.id, 0);
export default getStudentIdsSum;

const getStudentsByLocation = (arr, city) => arr.filter((student) => student.city === city);
export default getStudentsByLocation;

import createInt8TypedArray from './5-typed_arrays';

console.log(createInt8TypedArray(10, 2, 89));

import setFromArray from './6-set.js';

console.log(setFromArray([12, 32, 15, 78, 98, 15]));

const setFromArray = (arr) => new Set(arr);
export default setFromArray;
